headline: Cover Whale Announces $40 Million in Growth Equity Financing from Morgan Stanley Expansion Capital to Fund Growth Initiatives
summary: NEW YORK, July 28, 2025--Cover Whale Insurance Solutions, Inc., a leading insurtech specializing in connected insurance for commercial auto, announced $40 million in new equity financing from Morgan Stanley Expansion Capital. The financing will enable Cover Whale to accelerate investments in its technology platform, analytics, and expand its product offerings to drive increased growth and profitability.
